{"tid":1391483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世]全部人同我入黎學戴頭盔眼罩","createTime":"2019-07-31T12:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T16:10:01.000Z","uid":8948,"like":62,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"c6a6844718c8ccce7b51482748e213860a4e7558","tid":1391483,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:34:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">首先好多謝大家有勇氣企係最前守護香港<br />\n<br />\n但係！係守護香港之前，係守護其他手足之前，必定要守護好自己既生命<br />\n</span><br />\n黑警已經放風會出水炮車，各位既防護用具唔可以再缺，亦唔可以再戴錯，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>否則會令你受既傷更嚴重<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n請各位堅守以下兩大原則：<br />\n１。企第一排必定要有頭盔+眼罩+盾牌+護手護腳+護甲( 最少最少要背囊揹前，塞少少衣物同水樽入去)<br />\n<br />\n２。除非你係後勤，否則都必須要戴頭盔避免流彈擊中頭部造成嚴重受傷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>頭盔一定要有帽帶帽帶帽帶，確保受到第一擊之後頭盔都唔會飛脫</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n即刻用20秒學下點帶，係屋企調整好帽帶既長度先好出街<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oshc.hk/videos/1775100815919147\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foshc.hk%2Fvideos%2F1775100815919147&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFj11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=ddabc9f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oshc.hk/videos/1775100815919147</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">眼罩：絕對唔可以用細泳鏡，至少要用潛水鏡潛水鏡潛水鏡</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.goma.com.hk/content/product/300_10S-CF6100M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.goma.com.hk%2Fcontent%2Fproduct%2F300_10S-CF6100M.jpg&h=fed807f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩大原則<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">１。邊位一定要係橡膠邊，以求密封隔煙<br />\n２。戴上之後，用力按，受力位一定要係眉骨同顴骨受力為之合格</span></span><br />\n<br />\n受到衝擊個陣，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">細泳鏡會導致你眼窩眼球受極大壓力，有可能致盲或眼球突出</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀<br />\n【水炮車】台灣人教你點保護自己<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1391410\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1391410</a><br />\n<br />\n[+防50] 木盾加膠片可以擋海綿彈同橡膠彈<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dtEjmS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dtEjmS</a><br />\n<br />\n8月2日，8月3日，8月4日，8月5日<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1391041\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1391041</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/7RN16bQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7RN16bQ.png&h=a2dede95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bad79852435822d683394b4ea750f20b189aa3be","tid":1391483,"uid":8948,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:34:36.000Z","msg":"八月五，我要罷工"},{"pid":"0885a3c54a2c634ae41b4cd0a4671e1df9147fc8","tid":1391483,"uid":179979,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:36:55.000Z","msg":"諗唔到有咩理由仲要返工"},{"pid":"3ca117c23b63eb1de7b23fcd2ef4a2b9e27ecbae","tid":1391483,"uid":253826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:39:21.000Z","msg":"［請廣傳]大量文宣！大量文宣！大量文宣！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1390733\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1390733</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4a9b5454f6caef236c30f4e7aa537f1e69024b7a","tid":1391483,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:43:54.000Z","msg":"八月五，我要罷工"},{"pid":"74428c2dea4ee984a69127a66f90e08743cd82da","tid":1391483,"uid":267822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:46:38.000Z","msg":"學識左 多謝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">根據警察通例20章14條要求你出示委任證<br />\n否則<br />\n根據香港法例第228章22條相信你干犯冒警罪行</span>"},{"pid":"f582ddf514ecdb01508fab9ed53dee1ca63f97fe","tid":1391483,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:4