kg/abDpOOU</a><br />\n<br />\nTG group<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/OmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FOmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFj11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=262e7e0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/OmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA</a>"},{"pid":"4e9c95b7a2bebcb32ea4fba1f9db20ec187897c7","tid":1391483,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:27:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b636b3f035bb6fd115c8fac54d3db5c02bcb93fc","tid":1391483,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:36:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81704fb5152bbcac61e20049c8ae813e7af67179","tid":1391483,"uid":159002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:36:43.000Z","msg":"[拋磚引玉] 外國出手不是夢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1391709\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1391709</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7b5ad485f68afbf0c87d25eaa857210316fbd7c2","tid":1391483,"uid":78414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:26:55.000Z","msg":"8月1 中環金融界集會<br />\n8月2 公務員集會<br />\n8月3 旺角遊行<br />\n8月4 將軍澳1330集合， 港島西1600出發<br />\n8月5全民大罷工<br />\n<br />\n文宣要做足，airdrop連儂牆發映會傳單<br />\n<br />\n重申五大訴求<br />\n徹底撤回逃犯條例修訂<br />\n收回612暴動定性<br />\n釋放及永不檢控所有被捕抗爭者<br />\n成立獨立調查委員會 徹底追究警察濫權<br />\n即時解散立法會 全面實行真雙普選"},{"pid":"58e00e94b768d22b4d13aec761ced62ff152d99e","tid":1391483,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:42:47.000Z","msg":"全民8月5日大罷工！五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選一定要排最頭，仲要好似美國咁設時限係2020年內落實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n當新移民夠多，雙普選自然會落實，港共明顯會用偽民主反真港人<br />\n（雖然係舊post，但都想人諗下，一定要止左血先）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1328467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1328467</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立</span>呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私啦，過埋2047都嗰頭近啦，之後再算啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭，仲要設時限，最好2020年內！"},{"pid":"d87281139d7420129384b7f0de771c77fdf71e04","tid":1391483,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:16:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7da78df7ba7c54616ef9474c10eaa0a36ed8b55d","tid":1391483,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a84e81f85e90c0ab3ccb7c973c9a5c97ffccf0e2","tid":1391483,"uid":36008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:17:49.000Z","msg":"Aeon $12店搵到呢個，賣$30，有黑色/深灰<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S1SYz1Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbna